COMMERCIAL MODULES NOTICE
=========================

The EOM Volumetric Auditor (src-tauri/src/commands/eom.rs and related
modules) is a commercial module that requires a license key for signed
report generation. The source code is open under the MIT license above,
but generating signed EOM audit reports requires a valid license issued
by the maintainer. See SECURITY.md and src-tauri/src/mining/license.rs
for the license verification scheme.

This "open core" model means:
  - The processing engine, frontend, and standalone binaries are free
    to use, modify, and redistribute under MIT.
  - The EOM Auditor's signed-report feature is gated by a license check.
    Unsigned reports can be generated without a license for evaluation.
  - Future Pro plugins and commercial extensions will be proprietary.
